skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Listen to weekly walking tour suggestions from Take A Walk Through History With Us. We start all of our tours from the First Nations Sculpture Garden in downtown Rapid City as we help visitors experience the shared history of the Black Hills, both settler and Indigenous. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
